        "description": "Weather sensor:\n\nOp basis van lat lon coördinaten kunt u de neerslag twee uur vooruit ophalen in tekst vorm. 0 is droog, 255 is zware regen. \nmm/per uur = 10^((waarde -109)/32) \nDus 77 = 0.1 mm/uur\n\n\n<h4> some classification </h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Very light rain\tprecipitation rate is < 0.25 mm/hour</li>\n<li>Light rain\tprecipitation rate is between 0.25mm/hour and 1.0mm/hour</li>\n<li>Moderate rain\tprecipitation rate is between 1.0 mm/hour and 4.0 mm/hour</li>\n<li>Heavy rain\trecipitation rate is between 4.0 mm/hour and 16.0 mm/hour</li>\n<li>Very heavy rain   \tprecipitation rate is between 16.0 mm/hour and 50 mm/hour</li>\n<li>Extreme rain\trecipitation rate is > 50.0 mm/hour</li>\n</ul>",
